Financial Reports for Taxes 
bookmark_border
On this page
Tax withholding

These are the financial reports available for tax-related data.

Tax withholding

This report contains tax withholding information for a content owner.

The reportType id for this report is content_owner_tax_withholding_a1.

Contents
Primary Key:
adsense_earnings_month

Additional fields:
channel_id
revenue_source
local_currency
total_revenue_by_source
us_sourced_revenue
tax_withholding_rate
tax_withheld_amount
